==English==

===Pronunciation===
The pronunciation of gyros/giros/<B>GREEK SPELLING HERE</B> varies widely, even having dialect variation in Greece.

The pronunciation [[WEAE]] /ˈyi.ɹoz/ is promoted on advertising posters in many restaurants; /ˈyi.ɹo/ (the ''s'' is silent) is probably the most authentic (that is, sounds most like the Greek but uses only American English sounds).  The completely Anglicized pronunciation is /ˈʤaɪ.ɹoz/.

See [http://www.linguistlist.org/issues/6/6-1641.html] for a survey of pronunciations in various regions.

